As a player I want to type in my initials so I can be represented in the leader board.
As a player I want to choose how many dice to roll so that I can get close to my goal of 23, without going over.
As a player I want to roll so that my dice can be added in the game and get closer to the score of 23.
As a player I want to choose to not roll so that I can maintain my score before going over the score of 23. 
As a score keeper I want to set the score so that I can declare a win or loss when reaching or exceeding 23.
As a score keeper I want to get the score so that I can provide the values to the leaderboard.
As a player I want to view the leader board so that I can see mine and others' overall scores.
As a player I want to view my personal statistics so that I can see my average number of rolls per turn.
As a player I want to view others' statistics so that I can compare my average number of rolls per turn with theirs.